    <title>SAP Build Apps How to call Odata resource with Expand</title>
    <updated>2025-03-07T12:11:40.409000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>RahulKumar04570</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1475783</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi&amp;nbsp; ,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I need a help in SAP Build App to get and display data from the SAP Odata v2 services&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Gateway OData Query:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;/ZGSP_INSPECTION_OPERATION_SRV/INSPOPER_GETDETAILSet(Inspoper='0010',Insplot='045000001552')?$expand=GetCharResults&amp;amp;$format=json&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Connected odata services ZGSP_INSPECTION_OPERATION_SRV&amp;nbsp;with BTP Destination&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RahulKumar04570_0-1741343216701.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/234398iE606726F49FC87A0/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RahulKumar04570_0-1741343216701.png" alt="RahulKumar04570_0-1741343216701.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RahulKumar04570_1-1741343252392.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/234400i8D110E7C1BDDFE31/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RahulKumar04570_1-1741343252392.png" alt="RahulKumar04570_1-1741343252392.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="RahulKumar04570_2-1741343300551.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/234401i08CF112F1516D002/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="RahulKumar04570_2-1741343300551.png" alt="RahulKumar04570_2-1741343300551.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;How to call below query to get and display data in list view?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;call&amp;nbsp;ZGSP_INSPECTION_OPERATION_SRV/INSPOPER_GETDETAILSet(Inspoper='0010',Insplot='045000001552')?$expand=GetCharResults&amp;amp;$format=json&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/questions-about-sap-websites/sap-build-apps-how-to-call-odata-resource-with-expand/qaq-p/14036817"/>
